
 Datasets
1. gefcom.csv
Benchmark-style energy forecasting dataset inspired by GEFCom.

Includes variables such as:

temperature
wind speed
solar irradiance
load demand
2. nasa_power.csv
Weather data collected from NASA POWER API.

Includes:

temperature
wind speed
solar irradiance
3. synthetic_energy.csv
Constructed dataset used for reproducible experiments.

Target variable:

energy_output
